-- Putin Blames Corruption, Police for Spread of Russia Nationalism
-- B y   I l y a   A r k h i p o v
-- 2012-08-24T16:53:11Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-08-24/putin-blames-corruption-police-for-spread-of-russia-nationalism.html
President  Vladimir Putin  blamed
corruption and negligence among law enforcement for the spread
of inter-ethnic conflicts in Russia.  “Corruption, prejudice and the inability of the
authorities to guarantee justice and protect human rights are
the drivers of inter-ethnic tensions,” Putin said today at the
first meeting of his Council for National Relations in Saransk
in the Volga region.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Ilya Arkhipov in Moscow at 
